{"tid":160630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台北為何像貧民窟？醜到爆的招牌、鐵窗其實都是台灣人自私心態造成的","createTime":"2017-03-18T01:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T04:14:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9628b009ecd90330bca6f38824d89efde8bf1eec","tid":160630,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://buzzorange.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96-31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F%25E6%2593%25B7%25E5%258F%2596-31.png&h=dc5fafe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n走在房價誇張貴的台北街頭，表面上大樓、豪宅林立，然而轉個彎就可見違章建築、頂樓加蓋、鐵窗外、腐蝕剝落的牆面、暴露的電線、凌亂的招牌&hellip;一一映入眼簾，「美感」二字在此可以說是被徹底摧毀殆盡。<br />\n<br />\n原本一棟還不會太醜的公寓，每戶都弄不一樣的鐵窗，除了破壞市容以外，還自我阻隔了火災逃生機會。<br />\n<br />\n還有，台灣人蓋房子或設計招牌時，超愛用鮮紅、亮黃、花花綠綠等飽和度超高的鮮豔色彩隨意拚搭，讓人眼花撩亂。去看看日本街道為什麼能清爽素雅，他們幾乎不太用這些過度飽和的顏色。<br />\n<br />\n建築風格上，也是雜亂無章，中國風、日本風、歐洲風、簡陋風大亂鬥。在台北街頭，你容易看到一棟巴洛克古蹟建築旁，蓋了一棟大理石商業大樓，然後在商業大樓旁，搭了一間鐵皮麵攤。<br />\n<br />\n曾經有外國人到台灣後訝異台北的市容如此恐怖，還拍影片控訴台北宛如貧民窟：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LOSW44yBxzM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLOSW44yBxzM&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6tU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4bf6a5eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LOSW44yBxzM</a><br />\n<br />\n為何台北明明就是台灣的首都，市容卻如此老舊雜亂不堪，看上去像個巨大貧民窟呢？<br />\n<br />\n有網友在 PTT 發文指出，這是因為「增加自身利益」、「方便」、「節省帳面開銷」是台灣多數人的價值觀。他說，在台灣人的心目中，美感、機能安全性、公眾利益等價值通常較不重要。<br />\n<br />\n有什麼樣價值觀的居民就會產生甚麼樣的街景，其實不只台北，基本上整個台灣都是如此。像是大樓隨處可見陽台外推、裝鐵窗，甚至頂樓加蓋（明明違法，還敢出租房客），這些都是為了增加個人的使用空間、擴大自身利益，但卻犧牲了美感、機能安全性和公眾利益。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n商家招牌搶佔街道的天際線、利用突兀刺眼的燈光吸引顧客，就是為了增加收入而犧牲美感和用路人的安全；商家占用騎樓、堆放商品、清洗食材，一樣，犧牲美感和安全成就自己的利益；巷道違規停車，車主抱持著沒被開單能省停車費心態，只為了自己方便省時。<br />\n<br />\n在台灣常見到大樓外牆磁磚剝落傷到人的事件，但對多數人來說，不管是修外牆、洗外牆都要錢，更多人寧願用來換手機、換新車 ， 而不是住戶集資改善公共空間。<br />\n<br />\n這些族繁不及備載的空間不當使用，其實都反映了行為者的價值觀。整體來說，比起公眾利益，台灣人更在乎自己，做事只求增加自身利益。想要擺脫醜陋市容，台灣人勢必要從根本改變自私的心態。"},{"pid":"5f7be6bfa23a4895f78402a798af5a6351d26796","tid":160630,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:04:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/2017/03/16/ugly-city-like-a-slum/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2Fugly-city-like-a-slum%2F&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6tU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=61e0d2e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/2017/03/16/ugly-city-like-a-slum/</a>"},{"pid":"7cd2e4f0582d5d2b283644fdd84689bad0b7e9c3","tid":160630,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:21:45.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地鬼佬話你兩句slum你就當正係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畀小小critical thinking啦台仔"},{"pid":"5ee793ed4fabc18ccf6f53d75cec844648f6f6df","tid":160630,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地鬼佬話你兩句slum你就當正係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畀小小critical thinking啦台仔</blockquote><br />\n跟住有d台仔又要乘機批鬥自己人，又自私，乜乜價值觀.....................<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf1a5d6a3b93d4ade4f89b1c79f970d697e4d21","tid":160630,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地鬼佬話你兩句slum你就當正係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畀小小critical thinking啦台仔</blockquote><br />\n跟住有d台仔又要乘機批鬥自己人，又自私，乜乜價值觀.....................<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑乜鬼，呢啲招數港豬贏台仔幾條街"},{"pid":"401bd6b2887adb1bdbfb90ccaf351053aacd514d","tid":160630,"uid":66483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:28:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家"},{"pid":"04cbfeaf5f34b713909c49ca862f41897646af6c","tid":160630,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T01:56:31.000Z","msg":"作者緊係未去過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢d係特色黎，正如香港既唐樓"},{"pid":"c168d2084ab0755e85fa9f999ca0b171619f7fc6","tid":160630,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb765ee32c4eca8fa228bccc6d203563f09b914","tid":160630,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作者緊係未去過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢d係特色黎，正如香港既唐樓</blockquote><br />\n佢應該中意整到星加坡咁齊輯輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(所以星加坡畀人話無文化)"},{"pid":"01caa8bc782c0947e940518968fc717f0183c885","tid":160630,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:45:48.000Z","msg":"咁老實講，台北真係好垃圾，連深圳都比唔上"},{"pid":"77ba552970398f3e506aaf220c02ad9cba08a566","tid":160630,"uid":77697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁老實講，台北真係好垃圾，連深圳都比唔上</blockquote><br />\naggre<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a19fde53e426de53ec16b62766d9b66cf49d9f4","tid":160630,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:49:13.000Z","msg":"咁台灣人事實上真係又自私又無恥啵"},{"pid":"f06485b9d2e3202e4c67897118f4697f65bc1a41","tid":160630,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>作者緊係未去過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢d係特色黎，正如香港既唐樓</blockquote><br />\n佢應該中意整到星加坡咁齊輯輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(所以星加坡畀人話無文化)</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd舊屋，唐樓，劏房都有人吹奏<br />\n真係有文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難怪話香港人抵撚死<br />\n自己壓逼自己人<br />\n原來係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082e8f1bbfeabb4f7db3e672dbef6e7b8696def3","tid":160630,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLUN0ue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLUN0ue.jpg&h=c76aa92b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自卑就自卑啦台灣仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd70b019d8ba579d4049f55d668faac1e7ebb7e","tid":160630,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地鬼佬話你兩句slum你就當正係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畀小小critical thinking啦台仔</blockquote><br />\n跟住有d台仔又要乘機批鬥自己人，又自私，乜乜價值觀.....................<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑乜鬼，呢啲招數港豬贏台仔幾條街</blockquote><br />\n講起愛面子、玻璃心呢樣野真係蚛港台一家親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n遊客玩殘鶴咀海岸保護區　研究員：海螺被反轉　水泵被關掉　實驗或須遷走 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/154504/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/154504/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n港